SENATE BILL No. 69
_____
DIGEST OF SB 69 (Updated February 11, 2026 1:54 pm - DI 140)
Citations Affected: IC 36-8.
Synopsis: 1977 pension and disability fund. Increases the lump sum
death benefit payable to the heirs or estate of a 1977 fund member.
Provides that a 1977 fund member may extend their deferred retirement
option plan (DROP) retirement date up to 60 months after the member
entered the DROP. Makes conforming changes.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Rogers, Goode, Doriot, Donato,
Niezgodski, Pol Jr.,
Randolph Lonnie M
(HOUSE SPONSOR — VANNATTER)
